reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 159/96: DEEMING ORDER (MANITOULIN PLANNING BOARD)
reg_info.act_under: Planning Act   Loi sur l’aménagement du territoire

content.content: 1. (1) Ontario Regulation 672/81, as it read immediately before its revocation under section 2, shall be deemed to be and to always have been a by-law of the Manitoulin Planning Board under section 34 of the Act. O. Reg. 159/96, s. 1 (1). (2) The deemed by-law shall be referred to as by-law number 96-01 of the Manitoulin Planning Board. O. Reg. 159/96, s. 1 (2).
content.raw_html:
1. (1) Ontario Regulation 672/81, as it read immediately before its revocation under section 2, shall be deemed to be and to always have been a by-law of the Manitoulin Planning Board under section 34 of the Act. O. Reg. 159/96, s. 1 (1).

(2) The deemed by-law shall be referred to as by-law number 96-01 of the Manitoulin Planning Board. O. Reg. 159/96, s. 1 (2).

content.content: 2. Omitted (revokes other Regulations). O. Reg. 159/96, s. 2.
content.raw_html: 2. Omitted (revokes other Regulations). O. Reg. 159/96, s. 2.
